{"word":"ἀνταμείβομαι","slug":"ἀνταμείβομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνταμείβομαι</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <i>to exchange</i> one thing <i>with</i> another, <el>τί τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Archilochus Lyricus'>Archil.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <a href='S:person, personal'>pers.</a> <i>to repay, requite, punish</i>, <b><a href='S:Archilochus Lyricus'>Archil.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><i>to answer again</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; <el>ἀντ. τι πρός τινα</el> <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}